<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0749002" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0749002">樂阿蘭那行者 Araṇāvihārin.</note>
<note n="0749004" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0749004">不＋（不也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0750004" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0750004">發大乘者 Agrayāna saṃprasthita.</note>
<note n="0750005" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0750005">發最上乘者 Śreṣṭayāna saṃprasthita.</note>
<note n="0750006" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0750006">樂小法者 Hīnādhimuktika.</note>
<note n="0751001" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0751001"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->提＋（心）【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note>
<note n="0751002" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0751002">提＋（心）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0751006" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0751006">（佛言）＋如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
