<note n="0752009" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0752009"><choice><corr>一切有為法如夢幻泡影如露亦如電應作如是觀</corr><sic><space quantity="0"/></sic></choice> Tārakā timiraṃ dīpo māyāvaśyāya budbudaṃ, svapnaṃ ca vidyud abhraṃ ca evaṃ draṣṭavyaṃ saṃskṛtaṃ.</note>
